    "The parameters in Table 5.4 were generated foot_3 using Microsoft SEAL [SEA23].",
    "The high-level procedure for generating Table 5.4 is to set the modulus q to the maximum value supported for a given ring dimension, and then find the maximum multiplicative depth that can be achieved by examining the noise budget after decryption.",
